Description: cinda b. City Backpack Autumn Night Do you wish you could still carry a backpack but have definitely moved beyond the ho-hum, no-frills hiking/camping/high school variety? Well, thank goodness for cinda b's fabulous new City Backpack because now you can stop wishing and start enjoying a backpack with all the features you've been craving. Like all cinda b duffels, totes, handbags and accessories, the City Backpack has great design elements and a beautiful colorway. But this little gem has more than just good looks: it measures a perfectly portable 11.5" x 4.5" x 15.5" so it's got plenty of room but is sized just right for daily use; take it to work, the gym - even to class! There are 3 interior slip pockets for larger items (like notebooks, folders and the like) and an exterior zip pocket for keeping smaller items neat and tidy. And, to top it all off, the City Backpack has super-comfortable padded, quilted straps as well as sturdy grab-and-go webbing handles. The City Backpack is fashioned from a lightly padded, quilted nylon/poly fabric that is water resistant, stain resistant, 100% machine washable, surprisingly lightweight and extremely durable. So, when planning your next big adventure, cinda b's City Backpack is the perfect trekking companion! The cinda b family invites busy women everywhere to discover their beautiful collections of handbags, travel bags and accessories available on Amazon.
